---
// About Me section with desktop two-column layout
---

<section class="about-me" id="about">
    <div class="about-container">
        <div class="about-left">
            <h2 class="section-title">ABOUT ME</h2>
            <div class="about-image">
                <img src="/img/aboutme.png" alt="Carolina Lieja" />
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="about-right">
            <div class="about-intro">
                <p class="about-text">
                    Design is my way of asking better questions.<br />
                    <strong
                        >The answers? They're the kind that make people stop
                        scrolling.</strong
                    >
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="experience-section">
                <h3 class="subsection-title">EXPERIENCE</h3>
                <p class="section-text">
                    I'm a Devine student at Howest â€” a digital designer who
                    thinks in color, code, and curiosity. I live in the space
                    where design meets technology, crafting interactive
                    experiences that feel as good as they look.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="between-lines-section">
                <h3 class="subsection-title">BETWEEN LINES</h3>
                <p class="section-text">
                    I am someone who thinks a lot, cares a lot, and creates from
                    that place. I am curious about people, nature,
                    stories, anything that makes the world feel a little more
                    meaningful. I like slow discoveries, small surprises, and
                    ideas that grow into something bigger. Design is just the
                    way I translate who I am: thoughtful, playful, and always
                    exploring.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .about-me {
        background: #101010;
        color: #fff;
        padding: 0;
        border-top: 2px solid #fff;
        border-bottom: 2px solid #fff;
    }

    /* Fixed two-column layout with proper vertical divider */
    .about-container {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
    }

    @media (min-width: 1024px) {
        .about-container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            position: relative;
            /* Center the entire content block with balanced margins */
            max-width: 1600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 100px;
        }

        /* Vertical divider line between left and right */
        .about-container::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            left: 50%;
            top: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 2px;
            background: #fff;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
        }
    }

    /* Left column styles */
    .about-left {
        padding: 60px 20px;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 30px;
    }

    @media (min-width: 1024px) {
        .about-left {
            /* Center title and image together vertically */
            padding: 80px 60px 80px 80px;
            gap: 40px;
            justify-content: center;
        }
    }

    .section-title {
        font-family: "Space Grotesk", sans-serif;
        font-size: 72px;
        font-weight: 700;
        /* Center title text on mobile */
        margin: 0;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
        color: #fff;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .about-image {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 400px;
    }

    .about-image img {
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        display: block;
        filter: grayscale(100%);
    }

    /* Right column styles */
    .about-right {
        padding: 40px 20px;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
    }

    @media (min-width: 1024px) {
        .about-right {
            /* Adjust right padding for balanced spacing */
            padding: 80px 80px 80px 60px;
            justify-content: center;
        }
    }

    .about-intro {
        padding-bottom: 40px;
        border-bottom: 2px solid #fff;
        margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .about-text {
        font-family: "Space Grotesk", sans-serif;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 400;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin: 0;
        color: #fff;
    }

    .about-text strong {
        font-weight: 700;
    }

    .experience-section,
    .between-lines-section {
        padding-bottom: 40px;
        border-bottom: 2px solid #fff;
        margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .between-lines-section {
        border-bottom: none;
        margin-bottom: 0;
        padding-bottom: 0;
    }

    .subsection-title {
        font-family: "Space Grotesk", sans-serif;
        font-size: 32px;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin: 0 0 20px 0;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        color: #fff;
    }

    .section-text {
        font-family: "Space Grotesk", sans-serif;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 400;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin: 0;
        color: #fff;
    }
</style>
